kandi akaba umuvugabutumwa w'umunyarwanda wamamaye nk'umumisioneri kwisi hose 'muriki gihe<ref>https://awmamerica.org/about/</ref> ,uyu rero akaba ariwe muyobozi mukuru 
wa Authentic Word Ministries na Zion temple zose kwisi hose , n' umunyarwanda wavukiye muri [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|RDC]] yarizwi nka [[zayire]] cyangwase congo ,ubu akaba atuye muri [[Amerika]] ahazwi nka Dallas.

== Amateka ==
Apostle Dr Paul Gitwaza n' umunyarwanda wavukiye mucyahoze ari [[Zayire]], yari afite ababyeyi bombi umwe muribo ari umushumba ari se umubyara.

yigiyeyo amashuri abanza nyuma aza gukomereza muri Kenya aho yize ibijyanye n'indege , bigwako ari naho yahamagariwe kuza gutangiza umurimo w'

ivugabutumwa mu [[Rwanda]].

== Umuryango ==
Apostle Dr Paul Gitwaza yashakanye na Angelique Gitwaza babyarana abahungu batatu<ref>https://www.flickr.com/people/129783522@N04/</ref> Elisha, Luke na Davide 

abo bahungu bose bavukiye mu [[Rwanda]] , Gitwaza yashinze amatorero ya Zion temple arenga 123 mubihugu bitandukanye 

nko muri Afurika ni mu  Rwanda Burundi ,Kenya , Congo, Tanzania, Uganda ,aho yashinzemo imiryango 12 iba igize buri torero abereye umuyobozi.

== Imirimo ==
Paul Gitwaza yashinze imiryango itandukanye, harimo  Authentic world ministries<ref>https://web.facebook.com/drpaulgitwaza?_rdc=1&_rdr</ref> 

yashinze Radio na Television Authentic yashinze amavuriro ndetse n'imishinga ifasha abapfakazi n'imfubyi 

Dr Paul Gitwaza ubu niwe uhagarariye Alliance evangelical church mu Rwanda kuva mumwaka wa 2009.

